1. *Ubijaju* svinje za svinjska mesa. (They are killing pigs for pork meat.)
2. *Ubijali* su desetine ljudi. (They were killing tens of people.)
3. *Ubijanje* životinja je zabranjeno. (Killing animals is forbidden.)
4. *Ubijena* je jedna osoba. (One person was killed.)
5. Svi smo zgroženi zbog *ubijanja*. (We are all horrified by the killing.)